方对自己被「伤害」表达了歉意，而他感觉很不好意思拒绝这样的「好意」。我感觉他的心里好像就是 2 种极端，要么就是敌人，要么做朋友，而且很想把关系变成纯粹的友好，不能够处理和兼容「恩惠」和「仇恨」交错的人际关系，很容易因为一顿饭这样的小恩情忽略了之前的伤害，也不会去反抗，当恨别人的时候的报复手段也仅只是「不来往了」「不主动和仇人说话」… 仔细想想他好像对于同事也是这样，被欺负的时候恨别人，而当别人没脸没皮过来套近乎开开玩笑，或者给他个酸奶，他就淡忘了之前的仇恨；去甲方单位干活儿，对方提出不合理的要求导致他加班他觉得愤怒，但对方提出帮他打出租车时，他又很不好意思地客客气气，就很容易被拿捏… 这是什么心理？老实人这种心理又是怎样形成的？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-baff28f3998f134ffd1250d64b349f0c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "32 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652586232"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhMSk9cj2/Z8hEAMaCTEwNzI5NjY5OSDW1d2wBjAAOOgBQCRyCTY1MjU4NjIzMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1713237021.912553", "card_id": "Q_648902248", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 417}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "所以说青春的遗憾到底是什么呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "31 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/648902248"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhMSk9cj2/Z8hEAMaCTEwNjQ3ODA4NyCpj9evBjAAOPoDQCVyCTY0ODkwMjI0OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1713237021.912748", "card_id": "Q_653046599", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "职场新人如何最快地融入团队？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-98345a78456b583bd17ef733107c43ac_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "31 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653046599"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhMSk9cj2/Z8hE